title: Reverse List
description:
Write a function named `reverse_list` that takes in a list of items and returns a new list with the items in reversed order.

#### Function Signature
```python
def reverse_list(lst: List[Any]) -> List[Any]:
```

#### Input
- `lst` (List[Any]): A list of items of any type.

#### Output
- Returns a new list with the items in reversed order.
